<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DriveX · About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/login.css">
  </head>

  <body class="auth-body">
    <div class="auth-wrapper">
      <header class="auth-header">
        <div class="home-logo">
          <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="DriveX logo">
          <span>DriveX</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="auth-main">
        <section class="auth-card">
          <h1 class="auth-title">About Us</h1>

          <p class="auth-subtitle">
            DriveX is a modern land-vehicle dealership platform designed to make buying and selling vehicles easier than ever.
          </p>

          <div class="auth-form" style="gap: 14px;">

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>Who We Are</label>
              <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                DriveX was created with the idea of building a simple, intuitive, and reliable platform for vehicle enthusiasts and everyday drivers. 
                We focus on offering a clear and professional space where users can explore, compare, and discover cars and motorcycles in a fast and comfortable way.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>What We Do</label>
              <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                Our platform allows users to browse detailed vehicle listings with complete technical information, high-quality images, 
                and transparent pricing. Whether you are looking for a family car, a sports vehicle, or a powerful bike, DriveX helps you find the perfect match.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>Our Mission</label>
              <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                We aim to modernize the traditional dealership experience by combining technology and simplicity. 
                Our mission is to create a trusted environment where buying and selling vehicles becomes a smooth and enjoyable process for everyone.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>Our Values</label>
              <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Honest and detailed information for every vehicle.</li>
                <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Professional listings with accurate specifications.</li>
                <li><strong>Trust:</strong> A secure and reliable platform for all users.</li>
                <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Easy-to-use design focused on user experience.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Constant improvement and new features.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>The Team</label>
              <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                DriveX has been developed as a collaborative project by a passionate team of developers:
              </p>

              <ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Marcos Solano</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Pablo Craven</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Rodrigo Faure</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Ignacio Castillon</strong></li>
              </ul>

              <p style="margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Together we have combined our knowledge and creativity to build a platform that reflects our passion for technology and vehicles.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-field">
              <label>Contact Us</label>
              <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                If you have any questions, suggestions, or need assistance, feel free to contact our team. 
                We are always happy to help and improve your experience with DriveX.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>

        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="auth-footer">
        <p>DriveX · Los Del Fondo Devs · Málaga, 2025.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>